Steps to Unlock an Account(Screenshots are available for reference):
  1. Identify that the account is locked in the first place(an account will be locked based on the existing account lockout policy in your domain)
  2. Go to the Active Directory User and Computers tool tab
  3. Click on the locked account and go under the account tab
  4. Press unlock account and click apply
  5. The user will be able to try to login once again
